OL,3,CWelsh Government lose Supplementary
OL,4,CBudget vote
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has lost a
OL,7,Fcrucial vote on its spending plans,
OL,8,Fwith the main opposition leader saying
OL,9,Fit shows that "Plaid Cymru cannot
OL,10,Fgovern this country.''
OL,12,FFinance Minister Elin Jones said that
OL,13,Fher government remains "committed to
OL,14,Fdelivering (its) priorities" and will
OL,15,Fbring forward new plans in the Autumn.
OL,26,@qD@OOUuD@XOUvD@LpmvD@PpnvD@\O]
