OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784182683
OL,3,CWelsh Government lose Supplementary
OL,4,CBudget vote
OL,6,FReform UK, Labour and the
OL,7,FConservatives voted against the Plaid
OL,8,FCymru government's Supplementary
OL,9,FBudget following a heated and at times
OL,10,Fangry debate in the Senedd tonight. 49
OL,11,FSenedd members voted against it, 44
OL,12,Fvoted for it.
OL,14,FThe three parties accused ministers of
OL,15,Ffailing to act to build relationships
OL,16,Fwith other parties despite being in a
OL,17,Fminority government.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
