OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784182683
OL,3,CWelsh Government lose Supplementary
OL,4,CBudget vote
OL,6,FElin Jones said that "The
OL,7,FSupplementary Budget delivered #294m
OL,8,Fof extra funding to reduce NHS waiting
OL,9,Ftimes, expand childcare, and extend
OL,10,Ffree school meals.
OL,12,F"It contained no reductions to
OL,13,Fexisting services. It was about
OL,14,Fputting additional funding to work
OL,15,Fwhere it could make the greatest
OL,16,Fdifference to the people of Wales.
OL,26,@nD@VOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
