OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784182683
OL,3,CWelsh Government lose Supplementary
OL,4,CBudget vote
OL,6,FWelsh Labour has been holding out for
OL,7,F#100m to be spent in the current
OL,8,Ffinancial year.
OL,10,FThe Welsh Government offered first
OL,11,F#80m over two years, then #120m over
OL,12,Fthree years. Labour today rejected
OL,13,Fthat offer and urged the Finance
OL,14,FMinister to withdraw the supplementary
OL,15,Fbudget.
OL,17,FWhen the Welsh Government refused to
OL,18,Fwithdraw it, Labour resolved to vote
OL,19,Fagainst it.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
