CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784182683
OL,3,CWelsh Government lose Supplementary
OL,4,CBudget vote
OL,6,FFollowing tonight's vote, Reform UK
OL,7,FWales' leader Dan Thomas said,
OL,8,F""Tonight the Senedd said what Reform
OL,9,FUK has been saying since day one:
OL,10,FPlaid Cymru cannot govern this country.
OL,12,F"Rhun ap Iorwerth's government has now
OL,13,Flost the confidence of this Senedd on
OL,14,Fhis own budget. It's time he listened
OL,15,Fto the people of Wales rather than
OL,16,Flecturing them."
OL,18,FLabour's interim leader, Ken Skates
OL,19,Fsaid that, "It is deeply regrettable
OL,20,Fthat Plaid Cymru were not able to pass
OL,21,Ftheir supplementary budget.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOU{D@LOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784182683
OL,3,CWelsh Government lose Supplementary
OL,4,CBudget vote
OL,6,F"This isn't the outcome we wanted, but
OL,7,Fit's clear that the funding offered
OL,8,Ffor additional learning needs simply
OL,9,Fwasn't enough.
OL,11,F"This is about fighting for the best
OL,12,Fpossible deal for our schools and
OL,13,Fchildren and young people with
OL,14,Fadditional learning needs. We cannot
OL,15,Fsettle for less than they deserve.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
