OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784182683
OL,3,CWelsh Government lose Supplementary
OL,4,CBudget vote
OL,6,F"We urged the Plaid Cymru Government
OL,7,Fto withdraw their supplementary
OL,8,Fbudget, negotiate with the teaching
OL,9,Funions, and bring back another
OL,10,Fsupplementary budget in the summer
OL,11,Fwith more investment for additional
OL,12,Flearning needs.
OL,14,F"It's unfortunate that this was not
OL,15,Fthe approach they took, but there's
OL,16,Fstill time to negotiate and bring back
OL,17,Fnew proposals.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
