PN,43809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784182683
OL,3,CWelsh Government lose Supplementary
OL,4,CBudget vote
OL,6,F"As we've made clear, we do welcome
OL,7,Fmuch of the funding proposed in this
OL,8,Fsupplementary budget, particularly for
OL,9,Freducing NHS waiting lists, and we
OL,10,Fwant to see that extra funding
OL,11,Fdelivered."
OL,13,FThe Conservative finance spokesperson,
OL,14,FSam Rowlands said that "This budget
OL,15,Fhas the wrong priorities, offering the
OL,16,Fsame tired approach we saw under
OL,17,FLabour despite Plaid's promises of
OL,18,Fchange.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@KO]vD@XOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
