OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,439,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784182683
OL,3,CWelsh Government lose Supplementary
OL,4,CBudget vote
OL,6,F"There is nothing here to support
OL,7,Fsmall businesses, cut taxes, or
OL,8,Fkickstart economic growth. Once again,
OL,9,Four farmers have been overlooked, and
OL,10,Fnot a single penny of the extra
OL,11,Ffunding Wales received for Additional
OL,12,FLearning Needs (ALN) has actually been
OL,13,Fallocated to ALN support here."
OL,15,FIn itself this defeat won't be fatal
OL,16,Fto the Welsh Government's survival -
OL,17,Funlike a full budget - the Finance
OL,18,FMinister can table a new supplementary
OL,19,Fbudget.
OL,26,@uD@_O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
