OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1784182683
OL,3,CWelsh Government lose Supplementary
OL,4,CBudget vote
OL,6,FBut it is a blow and a reminder of how
OL,7,Fdifficult minority government can be.
OL,8,FUnless Plaid Cymru can reach deals in
OL,9,Fthe coming months and years, it will
OL,10,Fface a torrid time in the Senedd.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/11
